Jennifer Westfeldt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jennifer_Westfeldt 0 Jennifer Westfeldt (born February 2, 1970) is an American actress and screenwriter known for the 2001 independent film Kissing Jessica Stein, her 2004 Tony nomination for Wonderful Town, and her 2011 film Friends with Kids.
